'''Tagelda''' (S [[Tlatinit]] « ''regnum'' ») deg [[tamessartut]] amagnu, aswir n [[useggi afellay]] ugaren wiyaḍ nniḍen n [[Udus (tasnagmant)|udusen imuddiren]], ɣef ljal n ḍḍbayeɛ ucriken. Deg aseggi amaynu s kraḍ [[Taɣult (tasnudert)|tiɣula]], amnakel d aswir wis sin n useggi<ref name="Woese1977"/>{{,}}<ref name="Woese1990"/>.
Yal amnakel yettwabḍu s phyla. Isukfal imeẓliyen n useggi n tamessartut : tameddurt, [[Taɣult (tasnudert)|taɣult]], amnakel, [[Astirf (tasnudert)|astirf]], [[Asmil (tasnudert)|asmil]], [[Ammizwer (tasnudert)|ammizwer]], [[Tawacult (tasnudert)|tawacult]], [[Ṣṣenf (tasnudert)|ṣṣenf]] d [[talmest]].
Aceggeṛ n useggi yetwassumer sɣur [[Carl Woese]] deg useggwas 1990 sakin yunni-d imgerraden imeqranen deg uswir alayan 	ɣur [[Bakteria]] d [[Archaea]] ɣas ma snat tigrawin nni ttwassuddesent s udusen brukaryuta. Woese yebɣa ad yexdem anagraw n useggi s kraḍt tiɣula : Bakteria, Archaea d [[Eukaryuta]], tis kraḍt agi llan deg-es Leḥcawec, Iɣersiwen, Brutista d Igersalen. Aseqdac amiran n unagraw s sḍis imnukal yella d asemlili n unagraw 	amagnu s semmus imnukal d unagraw s kraḍt tiɣula n Woese. Anagraw agi s sḍis imnukal anda [[Brukaryuta|Monères]] qedderen s Bakteria d Archaea yuɣal d alugen deg aṭas n imuhal.
